text: @UPSHelp extremely disappointed. Sent package UK to US guaranteed to arrive yest’day for a wedding. Msg from customer today as not arrived. Package still in depot in UK! UPS cannot explain why. Appalling service

@sashandveil I understand your concerns regarding the delivery of the package. Please DM the tracking number, delivery address and contact phone number to the link provided so we can see what is going on. ^SB https://t.co/wKJHDXWGRQ
@UPSHelp I chose UPS as I trusted it would reach its destination in time for the wedding - I’m so upset

@UPS appalling customer service - my extremely urgent package was not delivered and no explanation as to why & no call or email informing it was delayed & I’m an account holder! Shockingly bad. I’ll never use #UPS again
